      "notes": "for garnish"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the fondue pot to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Add the olive oil to the fondue pot and saute the diced onion until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the diced aji amarillo peppers and cook for 2 minutes, until tender.",
    "Add the diced yellow potatoes to the fondue pot and cook for 10 minutes, until they start to break down.",
    "Stir in the crumbly reblochon cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the causa limena to a serving dish and garnish with chopped fresh cilantro."
